  "prompt": "How much should I expect to pay for a 1-car caltrain wrap advertisement?",
  "response": "The cost of a 1-car Caltrain wrap advertisement can vary based on several factors, including the duration of the campaign, the specific route, and any additional production costs. However, a general estimate for a 1-car wrap on Caltrain can range from $3,000 to $6,000 per month.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date pricing, I recommend contacting Caltrain's advertising department directly or working with an advertising agency that specializes in transit advertising. They can provide you with a detailed quote based on your specific needs and campaign goals.",
